---
title: Chinese-Style Speedy Beef Ramen Noodles with Garlic Chili Oil & Sesame Seeds
description: Dig into this fully loaded noodle bowl that takes less time to cook than it would to order takeout! Tender noodles are tossed with savory ground beef and crisp-tender cabbage and carrots, then coated with an umami-rich sweet soy glaze. It’s all sprinkled with scallions, drizzled with homemade chili-garlic oil for a kick, and finished with a shower of nutty sesame seeds for crunch—all in just 15 minutes!

